content_delivery.pdelivery1: We know that once you've picked the right shoe for your style, you'll want to get it as soon as possible.
content_delivery.pdelivery2: During the COVID-19 outbreak, we are doing our best to keep shipping and delivery times as accurate and up-to-date as possible. You can track the status of your orders online, quickly and easily, right at
content_delivery.pdelivery3: Our shipping offers free shipping on orders over $100 and many discount codes apply. Orders within the city are subject to same-day fast delivery, while suburban areas may take only 3-5 days to receive your order.
content_delivery.pdelivery4: We guarantee delivery to all provinces in the country and also have an international delivery service for an additional $15 delivery fee.
content_delivery.pdelivery5: You can click on the shopping cart in the upper right corner to display order information.
content_delivery.pdelivery6: We apply fast domestic delivery, it only takes 2-3 days for you to receive the goods. We will contact you when the order is about to be shipped to you.
content_delivery.ttdelivery7: What happens when I am not at home when the delivery arrives?
content_delivery.pdelivery7: We will put your order in stock and when you want to receive it you need to contact us via hotline: 09999185.
